What I have heard about the Alendar line is that there are 2 lines of spells (1 Cleric and 1 Chanter) that absorb a % of melee damage up to a maximum number.  For the main spell, I think that is 20% of damage up to 1600 HPs.  I see this as a very handy tool in the killing of boss mobs, particularly unslowable ones.  I understand the cleric version of the spell absorbs only 10% of the damage.<br>
<br>
My best guess on the reflect line is that this is a partial DA spell.  Lasts less time and may not be 100%.  Not sure if it actually reflects damage.<br>
<br>
Deception my best guess is a returned faction adjustment illusion.<br>
<br>
I have seen some commentary in the serverwide channel about Alendar.  Nothing about the other spells.<br>
<br>
